  (a1= 1, a2= 1): N =   0  (mod 3 = 0)
  (a1= 1, a2= 2): N =   1  (mod 3 = 1)
  (a1= 1, a2= 3): N =   4  (mod 3 = 1)
  (a1= 1, a2= 4): N =   9  (mod 3 = 0)
  (a1= 1, a2= 5): N =  16  (mod 3 = 1)
